Use the standard library
This is how to even_odd_count of num:
  Remember that text is tostring of abs of num
  Remember that evens is 0
  Remember that odds is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this text's length times:
    Remember that digit is toint of item i in text
    Remember that rem is remainder of digit and 2
    When rem is 0, then:
      Increase evens
    But, if not:
      Increase odds
    End when
    Increase i
  End do
  The answer is [evens, odds]
Now you know